ADDITIONAL NOTES:

This project is a modernization of the original Destruction II game,
adapted for modern Windows systems (10/11) with SDL2 compatibility layer.

The original game assets and code are property of Johan Torp/Nocturnal Development.
This modernization work is done with respect to the original creation.

